                            <comment id="12549152" author="stack" created="Thu, 6 Dec 2007 19:45:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Upped priority.  Needed in case where cluster is misbehaving and you need to rein it in w/o doing damage to your data.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12551655" author="musepwizard" created="Fri, 14 Dec 2007 00:23:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adds a shutdown hook to the regionserver to allow region servers to safely shutdown through a kill signal.  The hbase-daemon.sh script has been changed to allow shutdown of region server on the local box through the command &quot;bin/hbase-daemon.sh stop regionserver&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
